Package com.smartitengineering.domain.annotations

Annotation Types Summary
Eager This is meaningful if used with an associated resource, it signifies whether load the resource aggressively or on access of an non-id attribute.
Export This is to mark an associated resource with a policy on how to export, as an URI or object
Id A runtime annotation which will be used for identifying the attribute which will be used as ID in the URI for identifying a domain.
Name This mentions the name of the property to be used for exporting importing XMLs.
ResourceDomain This annotation should be used to mark a domain object as a resource.
